    answer: "Open your Instagram settings and convert to a Business or Creator profile — a free switch that links to your Facebook page. Electrical firms posting consumer unit upgrade sequences, neat first-fix containment runs, and EICR remedial before-and-afters generate strong local engagement — the visual contrast between a dangerous Wylex and a modern RCBO board is compelling content that homeowners save and share."
  },
  {
