    answer: "Homeowners with old fuse boxes, failed EICRs, and flickering lights after studying your upgrade portfolios. Landlords seeking EICR programmes after seeing your commercial testing work. Self-builders wanting full electrical packages. Architects studying your containment standards and luminaire installations for specification purposes."
  },
  {
    question: "How quickly does the AI respond to electrical DMs?",
    answer: "Each DM generates a response within seconds. Instagram's read confirmation establishes your electrical firm as immediately responsive. A homeowner who has photographed their scorched consumer unit and finally reached out to a qualified electrician needs swift engagement — not an unread message accumulating while anxiety about electrical safety grows."
  },
  {
    question: "What do Instagram DMs cost for electrical contractors?",
